title.rendered: WESTERN FILTERS Nissan Navara 2006-15 D40 2.5L TD YD25 (Spain Built) Pathfinder R51 – ProVent Vehicle Specific Catch Can Filter Kit OS-PROV-02-D40

content.rendered:
MANN+HUMMEL ProVent 200 Catch Can suits:

Nissan Navara D40 2.5L TD YD25 (2006-15)

Nissan Pathfinder R51

All Spain built Navara’s VIN numbers start with VSK… (etc).

This kit has everything you need to do the job, including the stainless steel bracket & all oil resistant hoses, the drain hose is also included. Highly efficient oil separation providing ideal protection for the turbocharger and other components installed downstream.

Provent Kit Includes:

:: Stainless Steel Bracket

:: Top & Bottom Hoses

:: Drain Kit

Click to view individual replacement parts.

MANN ProVent 200 Fitting Accessories >
